1) use a tree conrol (like in the Gaim properties dialog) on the left,
or an icon view (like in firefoxes properties)

2) include some pictures to help adjusting the monitor, for example a
black to white gardient, for brightness and contrast adjustments

3) grouping releated controls on a single page for example brightnes and
contrast are closely releated in my opinion.


