[snip]

Thanks for the report.

> I wish you version 1.0 :)

In fact we have no real plan to release version 1.0, but, one day, we'll
probably come to 1.0 .-)

> PS Could you tell me shortly how to translate ddccontrol to my language 
> (Polish) - I know that I should do something with .po file(s), what? 

Simply run in ddccontrol/po :
# msginit -i ddccontrol.pot -l pl_PL

Then add a line containing "pl" in LINGUAS.

(Then repeat the operation for ddccontrol-db)

To translate the strings in pl.po, I recommend "poedit", it is a very
nice tool.

BTW, if you are interested in maintaining the Polish translation, I'll
give you a CVS access so you don't have to rely on me to update the
files.

Best regards,

Nicolas



