Hi Roberto,

alpha and ia64 archs have never been tested, so I cannot give any 
warranty whether it will work, or not... ddcpci (the part that causes 
some problems to build on some archs) use at least one x86-specific 
function (ioperm), so I don't think this part of the code will work on 
alpha and ia64.

So, I would recommend that you restrict the package to x86 and amd64, 
which have been fully tested.

Best regards,

Nicolas


