please find attached an XML entry for the NEC2080 UX.
Obviously, the existing NEC2080UX+ file can be reused
for it, too. Main differences:

- Identifies as NEC6605
- Saturation *seems* to work for UX, at least in user
presets (shouldn't it for the UX+ too?)
